data.thought: S16|H|S15|Multi-system Phenotype C1: 'Intelligent ETL Pipeline'. Notebook orchestrates: (1) Firecrawl scrapes sources (2) Container runs data transformation (3) Database write via MCP (4) Slack notification on completion. Thoughtbox handles: schema inference, data quality checks, error recovery decisions, anomaly detection. Observable: pipeline DAG, data samples at each stage, AI reasoning about quality. Diff from Airflow: embedded reasoning, visual debugging, adaptive error handling.
